                            <comment id="17803894" author="JIRAUSER303078" created="Sun, 7 Jan 2024 02:24:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thank y&apos;all for reviewing and merging the changes.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=bschoeni&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;bschoeni&quot;&gt;bschoeni&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=smiklosovic&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;smiklosovic&quot;&gt;smiklosovic&lt;/a&gt; please review the second PR in the series: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/pull/3031&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/pull/3031&lt;/a&gt; This PR makes human-readable formatting default in `nodetool tablestats`. Are there unit tests and d-tests that I missed?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17811396" author="JIRAUSER303078" created="Fri, 26 Jan 2024 21:21:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=smiklosovic&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;smiklosovic&quot;&gt;smiklosovic&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=bschoeni&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;bschoeni&quot;&gt;bschoeni&lt;/a&gt; You guys are probably busy with Apache Cassandra 4.1.4 release. However, could you take a quick minute to help me understand why this work has stalled? And what can I do to un-stall it / get it moving again?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m waiting for someone to review this PR&#160; that makes human-readable output default in nodetool tablestats &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/pull/3031&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/pull/3031&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17811397" author="brandon.williams" created="Fri, 26 Jan 2024 21:24:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=zaaath&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;zaaath&quot;&gt;zaaath&lt;/a&gt; that would probably be better served in a new jira ticket at this point.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17811401" author="smiklosovic" created="Fri, 26 Jan 2024 22:01:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yes, this ticket served its purpose. Time to move on.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17811680" author="JIRAUSER303078" created="Sun, 28 Jan 2024 17:01:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Understood, thanks for explaining. I created a new Jira to make human-readable output default in Nodetool tablestats, see &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-19335&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;C-19335&lt;/a&gt; And I moved the code there &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/pull/3069&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;PR#3069&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
